00:24:17.875 --> 00:24:21.010
So women as they get
older begin to worry more

00:24:21.010 --> 00:24:23.750
about breast cancer and men
worry about prostate cancer.

00:24:23.750 --> 00:24:25.416
This is pretty
interesting, because this

00:24:25.416 --> 00:24:28.690
was 87 countries
participated in this research

00:24:28.690 --> 00:24:32.230
by the International Agency
for Research on Cancer.

00:24:32.230 --> 00:24:36.070
And they tracked animal
product consumption,

00:24:36.070 --> 00:24:39.160
and it correlated very closely
with 12 types of cancer

00:24:39.160 --> 00:24:42.440
but with a lag of
15 to 25 years.

00:24:42.440 --> 00:24:44.990
So cancer is not something
that shows up immediately.

00:24:44.990 --> 00:24:47.770
It takes a while for it
to grow in our bodies.

00:24:47.770 --> 00:24:51.430
And usually, in fact, you can't
even detect cancer in the body

00:24:51.430 --> 00:24:55.030
until it's been
growing about 10 years.

00:24:55.030 --> 00:24:57.670
