00:25:10.005 --> 00:25:12.640
The more calories from animal
foods that were consumed,

00:25:12.640 --> 00:25:15.400
the greater the incidence
of breast cancer,

00:25:15.400 --> 00:25:19.100
with a lag period
of about 20 years.

