And there are some
good things about it.

00:36:05.540 --> 00:36:08.081
It's similar to what we talked
about with the low-carb diets,

00:36:08.081 --> 00:36:11.080
which paleo is a type
of low-carb diet.

00:36:11.080 --> 00:36:13.740
No processed carbs,
sugar, and white flour.

