00:36:19.690 --> 00:36:22.000
that, well, when we were
in the paleolithic times,

00:36:22.000 --> 00:36:24.430
nobody was drinking the
milk from another mammal.

00:36:24.430 --> 00:36:27.340
That came later
with agriculture.

00:36:27.340 --> 00:36:30.800
And eating lots of fresh
fruits and vegetables.

00:36:30.800 --> 00:36:33.106
Typical good paleo
diet is going to have

00:36:33.106 --> 00:36:34.480
a plate full of
veggies, and it's

00:36:34.480 --> 00:36:36.730
going to have some
lean grass-fed beef

00:36:36.730 --> 00:36:40.786
