They've cut out the beans.

00:36:45.040 --> 00:36:47.120
They've cut out
the whole grains.

00:36:47.120 --> 00:36:49.800
A lot of times they cut out
the healthy starch foods,

00:36:49.800 --> 00:36:52.660
starchy vegetables
