00:50:27.390 --> 00:50:28.170
at Whole Foods.

00:50:28.170 --> 00:50:31.650
That definitely made it very
easy for me to become vegan.

00:50:31.650 --> 00:50:35.055
And it's definitely cheaper
than what I was eating before.

00:50:35.055 --> 00:50:36.180
And I feel a lot healthier.

00:50:36.180 --> 00:50:36.315
JOHN MACKEY: Good.

00:50:36.315 --> 00:50:38.817
So you're buying it doesn't
have to be expensive argument.

00:50:38.817 --> 00:50:39.400
AUDIENCE: Yes.

00:50:39.400 --> 00:50:42.020
It's definitely much,
much cheaper also.

00:50:42.020 --> 00:50:42.887
Yeah.

00:50:42.887 --> 00:50:44.970
If you think about like 1
pound of sweet potatoes,

00:50:44.970 --> 00:50:46.066
it's like $1--

00:50:46.066 --> 00:50:47.190
JOHN MACKEY: Yeah, exactly.

00:50:47.190 --> 00:50:48.420
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:50:48.420 --> 00:50:52.240
So when you talk about the
