AUDIENCE: I also like
don't directly support

00:53:53.650 --> 00:53:54.775
that disruption whatsoever.

00:53:54.775 --> 00:53:56.149
You know I just
understand what--

00:53:56.149 --> 00:53:57.410
JOHN MACKEY: OK, go ahead.

00:53:57.410 --> 00:53:58.090
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:53:58.090 --> 00:54:00.560
I have four housemates and
including my boyfriend,

00:54:00.560 --> 00:54:03.170
I have done investigations
into Whole Foods farms

00:54:03.170 --> 00:54:05.312
that claim should
be humane and--

00:54:05.312 --> 00:54:06.770
JOHN MACKEY: We
never claimed that.

00:54:06.770 --> 00:54:07.040
AUDIENCE: --cage free.

00:54:07.040 --> 00:54:09.895
JOHN MACKEY: Never claim any
of our things to be humane.

00:54:09.895 --> 00:54:10.520
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:54:10.520 --> 00:54:13.170
JOHN MACKEY: We just rate them
based on the animal welfare.

00:54:13.170 --> 00:54:15.640
It's a five-step program.

00:54:15.640 --> 00:54:17.390
We're not making a
claim that it's humane.

00:54:17.390 --> 00:54:20.960
We're just saying there are
different gradations of the way

00:54:20.960 --> 00:54:22.190
the animals are treated.

00:54:22.190 --> 00:54:23.550
Here's the thing.

00:54:23.550 --> 00:54:24.970
Is Whole Foods system perfect?

00:54:24.970 --> 00:54:25.770
No, of course not.

00:54:25.770 --> 00:54:30.650
We can't monitor
these farms 24/7.

00:54:30.650 --> 00:54:32.965
They have to pass certain
inspections and tests.

00:54:32.965 --> 00:54:34.580
And we do flunk them out.

00:54:34.580 --> 00:54:39.860
Really bad actors do get
investigated and tossed out.

00:54:39.860 --> 00:54:45.710
So all I can say is we're
the ones being attacked,

00:54:45.710 --> 00:54:47.630
and yet we're the
ones-- the only ones--

00:54:47.630 --> 00:54:49.730
that are trying to
do anything about it.

00:54:49.730 --> 00:54:50.420
Who else?

00:54:50.420 --> 00:54:52.840
You think Safeway is
doing anything about it?

00:54:52.840 --> 00:54:55.360
Do you think Trader
Joe's is doing--

00:54:55.360 --> 00:54:58.481
Trader Joe's still has
caged eggs for God's sake.

00:54:58.481 --> 00:54:59.230
We don't have any.

00:54:59.230 --> 00:55:01.490
We haven't had any caged
eggs for almost 20 years.

00:55:01.490 --> 00:55:04.640
We're the only ones that are
trying to make a difference.

00:55:04.640 --> 00:55:09.020
They're trying to get a higher
more ethical source of animal

00:55:09.020 --> 00:55:10.066
foods.

00:55:10.066 --> 00:55:11.690
And we're the only
ones being attacked.

00:55:11.690 --> 00:55:13.773
And we're being attacked
by the people that should

00:55:13.773 --> 00:55:15.110
be making common cause with us.

00:55:15.110 --> 00:55:16.996
They're not out there
picketing Safeway,

00:55:16.996 --> 00:55:19.370
and they're not out there
picketing Trader Joe's, they're

00:55:19.370 --> 00:55:21.470
picketing the only
company that's

00:55:21.470 --> 00:55:23.030
trying to make it better.

00:55:23.030 --> 00:55:24.910
I just think that's
incredibly weird.

