00:56:02.700 --> 00:56:03.410
I'm not the enemy.

00:56:03.410 --> 00:56:03.760
I'm a pragmatist--

00:56:03.760 --> 00:56:04.140
AUDIENCE: No, I agree.

00:56:04.140 --> 00:56:05.639
JOHN MACKEY: I'm a
pragmatist trying

00:56:05.639 --> 00:56:07.040
to make the world
a better place.

00:56:07.040 --> 00:56:09.350
But you have to meet the
