01:00:11.750 --> 01:00:15.000
We consider that to be
misleading to people.

01:00:15.000 --> 01:00:18.060
If you eat a whole foods
diet, mostly plants,

01:00:18.060 --> 01:00:20.060
you don't have to worry
about any of that stuff.

01:00:20.060 --> 01:00:21.230
You're going to
get enough protein.

01:00:21.230 --> 01:00:22.604
You're going to
get enough carbs.

